        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your connection to the denizens of the wilds grows ever stronger, and you find yourself able to speak with animals like you would in your native tongue. You can speak with all animals and beasts. If you have Animal Empathy, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to checks to Make an Impression on animals.",
